<L>__{exterior place de la bastille, paris day}
<T>__{superimpose caption:}
<D>__{nine years later}
<A>__{the dawn light glows on a massive elephant. the monument, made of wood and plaster, now ruined and crumbling, stands on a plinth on one side of the wide open square. on the far side, the remains of the great fortress that was the bastille. in the middle, scaffolding surrounds a half built triumphal column, which is being erected to celebrate the new regime.}
